      <ul xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<li><i>A Twist of Lemmon/Some Like It Hot</i> (1959)</li>
	<li>Piano Selections from <i>Irma La Douce</i> (1963)</li>
	<li>Piano and Vocals (1990)</li>
